                            激击之绮艺疾驰
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<p><em>Clash, gash, bash, ash, cash, mash, moustache&#8230;</em><br />
<em>激击、及剺、既刺、积渍、资之、糜矣、稀髭…</em></p>
<h1 id="toc0"><span><span class="ruby">激击之绮艺疾驰<span class="rt">Crash's flashy art-dash</span></span></span></h1>
<p><strong>嗨伙计们！欢迎来到我的艺作页！</strong>这里是我将要张贴所有我的SCP相关艺作的地方。<br />
我希望在这里更频繁地绘制和改进，所以但愿它能显现出来。</p>
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e3a6f7dbcc9/common--javascript/yahooui/tabview-min.js">
</script>
<div id="wiki-tabview-ca5ae5fb004c5b47182ea75551849499" class="yui-navset">
<ul class="yui-nav">
<li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>单独SCP篇目的艺作</em></a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:;"><em>GreenWolf 委托创作</em></a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:;"><em>非SCP 恐怖艺术</em></a></li>
</ul>
<div class="yui-content">
<div id="wiki-tab-0-0">
<p>这是所有专为单独设定的文章和/或它们之中我最喜欢的方面所画的艺作。</p>
<p>我会尽力去给大多数较新的SCP/我没看到有很多相关艺作的SCP作画，虽然我不排除偶尔的“经典作品”。虽然总的来说它也只是基于我最喜欢的。:D</p>
<p><strong>顺便说一下</strong>：如果你对没被我重视的SCP有任何建议，或者你是一个想拥有一些相关艺作的作者，我很乐意看看它们然后看看我能做什么！:D</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">禁忌之地</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">每次用时只要重复你又一次使用的任何名称的最后一个音节！Tabooboo&nbsp;Taboobooboo&nbsp;Tabooboobooboo。</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>以序号<strong>1</strong>开始，这儿是一个我至少每周思考一次的SCP：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1553042); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1553042&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595584730" alt="PeppersGhost" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1553042)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1553042); return false;">PeppersGhost</a></span>的<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/taboo">无名森林</a>。</p>
<img src="http://just-we.wdfiles.com/local--files/arts/GKqTfOt.jpg" width="600px" alt="GKqTfOt.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">4104</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">在他做了任何他想做的之后还有什么会留下来？</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>序号<strong>2</strong>是<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/krysalems" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4327863); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4327863&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595584730" alt="KrySalems" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4327863)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/krysalems" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4327863); return false;">KrySalems</a></span>的<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4104">“他欺骗了你们所有人”</a>。一个冷酷而怪诞、关于不存在的故事。</p>
<img src="http://just-we.wdfiles.com/local--files/arts/SPmasSr.gif" width="600px" alt="SPmasSr.gif" class="image" />
<p>这是我第一次真正以艺术的方式使用一张gif，所以我希望它能顺利出现。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">4444</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">老实说，在此之前我唯一知道关于戈尔的事是《南方公园》的描述。</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>这里来到了序号<strong>3</strong>！<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595584730" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;">djkaktus</a></span>的<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4444">布什vs戈尔</a>！</p>
<img src="http://just-we.wdfiles.com/local--files/arts/0LZY6tl.jpg" width="600px" alt="0LZY6tl.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">3596</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;Go,&nbsp;Go&nbsp;SJCAS!&nbsp;太不顺口了吧……</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>序号<strong>4</strong>是个关于超级英雄和星期六早晨的可爱故事：<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3596">SCP-3596</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/iamtheooga" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3942052); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3942052&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595584730" alt="IAmTheOoga" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3942052)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/iamtheooga" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3942052); return false;">IAmTheOoga</a></span>！</p>
<img src="http://just-we.wdfiles.com/local--files/arts/X5z78LS.jpg" width="600px" alt="X5z78LS.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">4005</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">It's&nbsp;an&nbsp;extra&nbsp;dimensional&nbsp;anglerfish&nbsp;ain't&nbsp;it?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>序号<strong>5</strong>是<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3337265); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3337265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595584730" alt="Tufto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3337265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3337265); return false;">Tufto</a></span>的<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4005">SCP-4005</a>。这篇对我来说非常有趣，因为它被描述成一个乐观、比较是“好结局”的故事，当它只让我渐生不适和恐惧的时候。</p>
<img src="http://just-we.wdfiles.com/local--files/arts/QWLNhd2.jpg" width="600px" alt="QWLNhd2.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Super&nbsp;Secret&nbsp;shit</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">它实际上是</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content"><img src="http://just-we.wdfiles.com/local--files/arts/6ZI3xpa.jpg" width="600px" alt="6ZI3xpa.jpg" class="image" />
<p>（来自我和我朋友服务器的截图）</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">4051</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">可怜的Rainer。</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>序号<strong>6</strong>对我来说很特别，因为我对一篇SCP的第一个想法，在加入这个网站之前，就是：“一个能从他穿的任何外套的口袋里拿出任何东西的家伙”。这篇基本上就是这样的概念但以一定的复杂性按比例实现，我永远也做不到。这就是<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4051">SCP-4051</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4665703&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595584730" alt="Nagiros" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4665703)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;">Nagiros</a></span>。</p>
<img src="http://just-we.wdfiles.com/local--files/arts/cjCPgLh.png" width="600px" alt="cjCPgLh.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">3165</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">当你可以有狼女孩的时候谁还需要狐女孩呢？</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>序号<strong>7</strong>我画了可怕的谋杀怪物而且让它不仅有趣而且还有点儿可爱。我想给她涂一些（畸形的）口红但它看起来只能像血。:(<br />
以及是的，我也会用颜色！:P 这就是<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3165">犬牙女</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dog-teeth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3116447); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3116447&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595584730" alt="Dog Teeth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3116447)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dog-teeth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3116447); return false;">Dog Teeth</a></span>！</p>
<img src="http://just-we.wdfiles.com/local--files/arts/NfICRgd.png" width="600px" alt="NfICRgd.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">4377</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">People&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;people&nbsp;god!</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
